    "4111203": {
        "Desc": "Get close and ascertain the situation",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is the guy on the floor sleeping?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "I believe so. I've tried everything, but he won't wake up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Looks like he touched the meteorite, just like the others..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "If by \"meteorite\" you mean the rock that struck the cart — worry not, I have dealt with that already using my magic."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "But by \"others,\" do you mean to say, there are others who have fallen into a similar slumber?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "One has witnessed with one's own Auge der Verurteilung the nightmarish slumber that proceeds forth from the Valley of Demonbone... It has caused great suffering for the humble peasants in the Vale of Springdom, many of whom still battle this wretched affliction even as we speak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "As mein Fräulein most eloquently describes, we have just come from Mondstadt, where many people have also fallen into an unwaking sleep. Their symptoms are identical to those of this poor gentleman here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Is that so... It appears these meteorites really made quite an impact."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Seems this guy is dressed like a Winery worker... And we've already met Ben — so this one must be Fritz!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Given that workers' attire has precious few distinguishing features, I must conclude that Paimon is blessed with exceptionally acute eyesight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Actually, Paimon's eyesight is normal, Paimon just has a really great memory! You're right, though, his clothes don't really stand out that much... Especially not compared to this guy over here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Haha, and by \"this guy over here,\" you mean me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yep! Paimon's never seen anyone dressed quite like you before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That huge hat is quite unique."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Those unique clothes are quite beautiful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "I am a vagrant from Inazuma. I had just stopped to assist this poor gentleman when you turned up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Are you investigating the aftermath of the meteorite strike?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, we were sent to help out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "I am Fischl, Prinzessin der Verurteilung, responding to the cry of my people in their hour of need!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "I am mein Fräulein's humble familiar, Oz the Raven."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And Paimon is an Honorary Knight of the Knights of Favonius's best friend!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Oh? Then you must be said Honorary Knight of said Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I am an adventurer of the Guild."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes, I'm the Honorary Knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Behold, my people, your beloved sovereign in the flesh! Do not despair, for judgment by Thundering Retribution is nigh, and it shall surely purge the seeds of nefarious nightmares that now sow chaos across the land!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Um... Excuse me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't mind her, just... y'know, let her do her thing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "She's a good egg, really."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Niu Zhi",
                    "T": "Excuse me! What's going on here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, great — good thing you're here, Mr. Millelith. This guy's fast asleep, and he won't wake up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Ah, it appears this is now in the hands of the Millelith — in which case, I am no longer needed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "It was truly a pleasure to meet you all. I have other matters to attend to now, so I shall take my leave."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Adventurers... I wish you every success in your endeavors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Bye-bye~!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, what happened was, we came here looking for someone, and found them..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Niu Zhi",
                    "T": "Thank you all for your cooperation. This victim is now in the care of the Millelith, and we will escort him safely to the <color=#00E1FFFF>disaster relief station</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Disaster relief station? You mean like a big tent with guards outside?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Niu Zhi",
                    "T": "Correct. We have established a <color=#00E1FFFF>disaster relief station</color> at <color=#00E1FFFF>Wangshu Inn</color>, where the unconscious victims of the meteorite strike can receive due medical attention."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "A wise decision by the Millelith."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon can't stop worrying about poor <color=#00E1FFFF>Fritz</color>... We should really go check up on him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Hmph... I suppose I shall deign to join you for one further excursion."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
